LOCALITY RECORDS (
<figureCitation id="71B52A0AFFF9FF98DB7AFB19F8F841AE" box="[1647,1824,1175,1212]" captionStart="FIGURE 69" captionStartId="37.[840,931,2673,2703]" captionTargetBox="[527,1888,1841,2662]" captionText="FIGURE 69.—Approximate range of the gruti group." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3828584" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3828584/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="19">
